name: Pylleo
body:
## Little Leonardo Toolbox
The Little Leonardo Toolbox is a collection of utilities for loading, calibrating, and filtering accelerometer data produced by accelerometer sensors developed by [Little Leonardo Co.](http://l-leo.com/eng/).

* [Documentation](pylleo.readthedocs.io)
* [GitHub repository](https://github.com/ryanjdillon/pylleo)

### Authors and Contributors
The code here has been written by Ryan J. Dillon (@ryanjdillon).
